data.description: Discover a charming 3-bed, 2-bath house tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac just blocks from Shawnee's vibrant business district. Ideal for investors or first-time homebuyers, this home offers a cozy living space that flows seamlessly into a well-appointed kitchen, perfect for hosting or daily living. Generously sized bedrooms and two bathrooms, including an ensuite, provide comfort and convenience. With a spacious yard awaiting your personal touch and a 2-car attached garage, this property offers both privacy and practicality. Enjoy its prime location near shops, dining, and local attractions, making it an excellent opportunity for those seeking a convenient and inviting space in Shawnee.
